## story/generated/ — Story System Exports
## ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
##
## FILES IN THIS FOLDER ARE GENERATED BY THE STORY SYSTEM.
## They override the hardcoded placeholder labels in story/*.rpy.
##
## ── HOW IT WORKS ────────────────────────────────────────────────
##
## The sandbox router checks for labels in this order:
##   1. gen_talk_[npc_id]    — generated version (this folder)
##   2. talk_[npc_id]        — hardcoded fallback (story/*.rpy)
##   3. talk_default          — generic stub
##
## Same pattern for actions:
##   1. gen_action_[location]_[action_id]
##   2. action_[location]_[action_id]
##
## And for meet scenes:
##   1. gen_meet_[npc_id]_first
##   2. meet_[npc_id]_first
##
## ── EXPORT CONTRACT ─────────────────────────────────────────────
##
## Each exported .rpy file MUST follow these rules:
##
## LABEL NAMING:
##   - Talk labels:     gen_talk_[npc_id]
##   - Meet labels:     gen_meet_[npc_id]_first
##   - Action labels:   gen_action_[location]_[action_id]
##   - Date labels:     gen_[npc_id]_date_[scene_id]
##   - Phone events:    gen_phone_[npc_id]_[event_id]
##
## EVERY LABEL MUST:
##   - End with `return` (never `jump` out — call stack safety)
##   - Set appropriate flags (flag_met_[npc_id] on first meet)
##   - Use `add_rel(npc_id, amount)` for relationship changes
##   - Use `add_stat(stat_name, amount)` for stat changes
##   - Use `show [npc_id] at [position] with dissolve` for sprites
##   - Use `hide [npc_id] with dissolve` before returning
##
## AVAILABLE HELPER FUNCTIONS:
##   add_rel(npc_id, amount)       — Adjust relationship (0-200)
##   get_rel(npc_id)               — Get current relationship value
##   rel_label(value)              — "Stranger"/"Acquaintance"/etc.
##   add_stat(stat_name, amount)   — Adjust any stat (clamped)
##   add_diary(text)               — Add diary entry
##   lc_show_phone()               — Show phone UI
##   lc_hide_phone()               — Hide phone UI
##   lc_text(channel, sender, msg) — Send phone text
##   advance_time(periods)         — Advance time forward
##
## AVAILABLE FLAGS:
##   flag_met_[npc_id]       — Set True on first meeting
##   flag_intro_done         — True after intro sequence
##   flag_therapy_started    — True after first Rivera session
##   flag_first_day_done     — True after completing day 1
##
## AVAILABLE STATS:
##   Core:        money, energy, happiness, intelligence, charm, fitness
##   Progression: trust, confidence, acceptance, curiosity
##   Body:        body_femininity, body_bust, body_hips, body_muscle, body_hair
##   Emotional:   love, lust, arousal, corruption
##   Appearance:  appearance_makeup, appearance_clothing
##   Social:      stat_public_presentation, stat_social_acceptance
##   Transform:   transformation_stage, hrt_started, hrt_day
##
## NPC IDS (use these exact strings):
##   Family:      mom, sister
##   Friends:     alex, maya, kai, theo, cora, sera
##   Romance:     luna, zane, nadia, ronnie
##   Professional:dr_rivera, dr_obi, prof_harlow
##   Community:   simone, reo, dom, jamie, river, sasha, petra,
##                august, arlo, eli, milo, oz, vesper, rio, dana,
##                ines, vivienne, camille, hana
##
